# Secrets / local paths

Do not copy into this repo:

- `~/.gmail-mcp/credentials.json`
- `~/.gmail-mcp/gcp-oauth.keys.json`
- `~/.openclaw/secrets.json`
- `~/.openclaw/gmail/unsubscribe_*.json` (may contain personal senders)
- Live `triage_seen.json` / session transcripts
- Filled-in `gmail.env` (use `.env.example` only)

`.env.example` uses placeholder hostnames and Slack channel IDs — replace on each host.
